Class wrapping steps of the automated merging process.

Usage:
    >>> lca = {}
    >>> first = {'foo': 'bar'}
    >>> second = {'bar': 'foo'}
    >>> path_limits = []
    >>> actions = {}
    >>> additional_info = {}
    >>> m = Merger(lca, first, second, actions,
    ...            path_limits, additional_info)
    >>> try:
    ...     m.run()
    ... except UnresolvedConflictsException:
    ...     # fix the conflicts
    ...     m.continue_run()
